1
00:00:18,166 --> 00:00:19,458
- Natsu:
PREVIOUSLY, ON "FAIRY TAIL."

2
00:00:19,541 --> 00:00:20,875
- Happy:
WHEW, I DON'T KNOW HOW

3
00:00:20,958 --> 00:00:22,541
WE DID IT, BUT WE
MANAGED TO STOP

4
00:00:22,625 --> 00:00:23,916
THE DRAGON CHAIN CANNON.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,583
- Lucy: UM, HELLO?
GIVE ME A LITTLE CREDIT.

6
00:00:25,666 --> 00:00:27,291
THINGS WORKED OUT
'CAUSE I SHOWED UP.

7
00:00:27,375 --> 00:00:29,291
- Natsu : YEAH, IT HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THE REST OF US.

8
00:00:29,375 --> 00:00:30,541
- Happy:
THEN I WANT CREDIT, TOO!

9
00:00:30,625 --> 00:00:31,875
I SAVED YOU, REMEMBER?

10
00:00:31,958 --> 00:00:34,083
I ALMOST BROKE MY BACK
'CAUSE YOU WEIGH A TON!

11
00:00:34,166 --> 00:00:36,916
- Lucy: YOU'RE GOING TO
GIVE ME A COMPLEX, CAT!

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,916
- ( theme music playing )

